03:34:12,757 --> 03:34:16,057
These archers, you're so annoying.

2064
03:34:16,057 --> 03:34:17,957
I mean, they die relatively fast if you crit them, but...

2065
03:34:17,957 --> 03:34:21,257
Yeah, they die relatively fast. ...archers are...

2066
03:34:21,257 --> 03:34:23,057
