2067
03:34:26,557 --> 03:34:28,057
You missed!

2068
03:34:34,157 --> 03:34:38,957
I said "you missed" and then... I got squished by the slime. Oh!

2069
03:34:39,257 --> 03:34:41,857
Kyuu... go... fu...?

2070
03:34:41,857 --> 03:34:44,757
How dare you! I'll avenge you!

2071
03:34:44,757 --> 03:34:48,457
The slimes! The slimes! The slimes!

2072
03:34:48,457 --> 03:34:49,657
4 seconds!

2073
03:34:51,957 --> 03:34:55,257
YAGOO, please! Where...

2074
03:34:55,257 --> 03:34:56,957
No!

2075
03:34:57,057 --> 03:34:58,657
All our lobby completely...

2076
03:34:58,757 --> 03:35:02,657
Time up...

2077
03:35:07,645 --> 03:35:08,945
Wow.

2078
03:35:10,245 --> 03:35:13,145
So how was that raid, Nino-Ina?

2079
03:35:13,245 --> 03:35:16,645
Ah, I got one common...

2080
03:35:16,645 --> 03:35:20,445
