2085
03:35:34,145 --> 03:35:40,445
You may put up something random for 278,940 Yen.

2086
03:35:40,445 --> 03:35:42,145
Two hundred...

2087
03:35:42,145 --> 03:35:43,645
Exactly.

2088
03:35:44,345 --> 03:35:47,345
Oh, is that the money you...

2089
03:35:48,145 --> 03:35:52,145
You can buy my books instead! I put some books.

2090
03:35:52,145 --> 03:35:54,445
No, no, no, I need this money...

2091
03:35:55,545 --> 03:35:57,545
No, I can't put any more stuff...

2092
03:35:57,545 --> 03:36:03,745
...'cause I hit the limit of the amount of stuff you can put up.

2093
03:36:04,445 --> 03:36:07,145
Okay, I'll buy one of this and then you can put up...

2094
03:36:08,045 --> 03:36:12,245
Okay, you can put up 211,264.

2095
03:36:12,545 --> 03:36:14,545
No! Buy them instead!

2096
03:36:20,445 --> 03:36:22,145
Anya... Ina...

2097
03:36:21,645 --> 03:36:24,145
あにゃ、いな。
Anya, Ina.

2098
03:36:23,445 --> 03:36:26,145
Hello アキ先輩！ / アキ先輩！
