2110
03:37:08,245 --> 03:37:09,645
1000万円。
10 million yen.

2111
03:37:09,645 --> 03:37:11,145
いいじゃない？
Isn't that good?

2112
03:37:11,145 --> 03:37:12,645
買っちゃう？
Should I buy it?

2113
03:37:12,645 --> 03:37:15,245
買っちゃえ！買っちゃえ！
Buy it! Buy it!

2114
03:37:16,145 --> 03:37:17,345
いいじゃない？
Isn't that good?

2115
03:37:17,345 --> 03:37:19,245
何でもだよ！
It's for anything!

2116
03:37:19,245 --> 03:37:21,645
何でもだよ、あにゃ！何でもって...
It's for anything, Anya! She said anything...

2117
03:37:21,645 --> 03:37:25,145
...何でもだよ。
...it's for anything.

2118
03:37:25,145 --> 03:37:29,645
1000万円はきついです。すみません、アキ先輩。
10 million yen is a bit much. I'm sorry, Aki-senpai.

2119
03:37:30,145 --> 03:37:33,945
あにゃはまだこの世界でトップを取ろうとしている？
Is Anya still aiming to take the top in this world?

2120
03:37:33,945 --> 03:37:37,145
え、さすがに無理だと思います。
Eh, I think that's logically impossible.

2121
03:37:37,145 --> 03:37:42,245
じゃ、1000万円買ったほうがお得なんじゃない？この...
Then, wouldn't buying it for 10 million yen be a bargain? In this...

2122
03:37:42,245 --> 03:37:44,145
ね、いな？
Right, Ina?

2123
03:37:44,145 --> 03:37:45,645
ね！
Right!

2124
03:37:45,645 --> 03:37:48,645
アキ先輩は狙ってるですか？トップを。
Aki-senpai, are you aiming for the top?

2125
03:37:48,645 --> 03:37:52,145
まあまあ、狙ってる。頑張ろうかなって。
Well, I am. I'm thinking of doing my best.

2126
03:37:52,145 --> 03:37:53,245
おおお...
Ooo...

2127
03:37:54,645 --> 03:37:56,145
なるほど。
I see.

2128
03:37:56,145 --> 03:38:03,145
いな、ちなみに、アキせんの何でもひとつ...いなめっちゃ金持ちだから、買ったら、いな？
Ina, by the way, Aki-sen's 'do anything' coupon... Ina, you're super rich, so why don't you buy it, Ina?

2129
03:38:05,645 --> 03:38:13,145
いなは...75,912円、だけ。どうですか？
Ina has... only 75,912 Yen. How about that?

2130
03:38:13,645 --> 03:38:15,145
7万？
70,000?

2131
03:38:15,145 --> 03:38:18,145
7万5千9百12円。
75,912 Yen.

2132
03:38:18,245 --> 03:38:23,245
あ、ちょっと7万円では聞けない...いな。
Ah, I can't listen to a request for just 70,000, Ina.

2133
03:38:24,345 --> 03:38:28,645
ええ？アキ先輩いいですか？こんなかわいいかわいいいなちゃんのお願いなんですよ。
Eee? Aki-senpai, is that okay? This is a request from the super cute Ina-chan.

2134
03:38:28,645 --> 03:38:35,145
いなのことはとってもかわいいし大好きな果んだけど、何でも...
I find Ina super cute and I love her, but doing anything...

2135
03:38:35,145 --> 03:38:37,645
そんなにかわいくないですか、アキ先輩？(笑)
Is she not that cute, Aki-senpai?

2136
03:38:37,645 --> 03:38:39,645
7万は...
70,000 is...

2137
03:38:39,645 --> 03:38:46,145
こんなかわいいかわいいいなのお願い...いいんですか？本当に。
Are you really okay refusing a request from this super cute Ina?

2138
03:38:46,245 --> 03:38:58,345
あにゃが1000万円で言うこと聞く券買ううんだったら、いなのお願いも聞いちゃおうかな。
If Anya buys the 10-million-yen 'do anything' coupon, maybe I'll listen to Ina's request.

2139
03:38:59,645 --> 03:39:08,245
それだったら...それだったら、500万、500万で済むんじゃないですか？一人。
If that's the case... if that's the case, wouldn't 5 million each make it work?

2140
03:39:08,245 --> 03:39:17,345
いや、1000万円からじゃないといけないんですかね？一個の...一個のお願いが1000万円だから。
No, does it have to start from 10 million yen? Because one request is 10 million yen.

2141
03:39:17,345 --> 03:39:18,645
ねええ...
Nooo...

2142
03:39:18,645 --> 03:39:20,145
...嫌だ。
...I don't want to.

2143
03:39:20,145 --> 03:39:22,645
嫌だなの？嫌だ...
You don't want to? You...

2144
03:39:22,645 --> 03:39:27,145
買って、買って... / 買ってよ、あにゃ、買って。
Buy it, buy it... / Buy it Anya, buy it.

2145
03:39:28,145 --> 03:39:33,245
何でも言うこと聞くよ。肩のマッサージもするよ。
I'll do whatever you say. I'll even give you a shoulder massage.

2146
03:39:33,245 --> 03:39:34,645
ええ？
Eh?

2147
03:40:03,686 --> 03:40:07,086
せーの、体売ってる！ / アーニャ、悪い日本語覚えちゃダメ。
One, two, she's selling her body! / Anya, you shouldn't learn bad Japanese.

2148
03:40:07,086 --> 03:40:08,786
そんな「体売ってる」、ダメなんですよ。
Saying \"selling body\" is a no-no.

2149
03:40:11,386 --> 03:40:12,486
体売って...
Selling body...

2150
03:40:12,486 --> 03:40:14,586
ダメなんですよ。
You shouldn't say that.

2151
03:40:14,586 --> 03:40:16,386
売ってないよ。
I'm not selling it!

2152
03:40:16,386 --> 03:40:18,586
なんでも言うこと聞く...
I'll do whatever you say...

2153
03:40:18,586 --> 03:40:21,486
おい、1000万で一人にだけ売ろうと思ってないよね？
Hey, you're not planning to sell her to just one person for 10 million, right?

2154
03:40:21,486 --> 03:40:23,986
あ、イナ、イナ、イナいない？
Oh, Ina, is Ina here?

2155
03:40:23,986 --> 03:40:25,686
イナ？
Ina?

2156
03:40:25,686 --> 03:40:26,786
イナ。
Ina.

2157
03:40:26,786 --> 03:40:33,786
イナとは、飲み物、いろんな飲み物を一緒に飲みたい共通点があるもんね、イナ。
We both share a love of wanting to drink different kinds of drinks, right, Ina?

2158
03:40:33,786 --> 03:40:35,086
はい。
Yes.

2159
03:40:35,086 --> 03:40:36,086
ね？
Right?

2160
03:40:36,086 --> 03:40:37,086
はい。
Yes.

2161
03:40:37,086 --> 03:40:41,886
1回に3種類とか4種類とか、いろんな飲み物を一緒に飲むのが好きだよね。
We love to drink like three or four different kinds of drinks at the same time.

2162
03:40:41,886 --> 03:40:43,586
そうですね。
That's right.

2163
03:40:43,586 --> 03:40:44,886
うん。
Yeah.

2164
03:40:44,886 --> 03:40:47,886
っていう、っていうことで、アキロゼがなんでも好きな飲み物買ってきてあげる。
So, Akirose will buy you whatever drink you like!

2165
03:40:53,786 --> 03:40:58,286
イナと会う時は毎回、好きな、その飲み物買ってきてあげる。
Every time we meet, I'll buy you that drink you like.

2166
03:40:58,286 --> 03:41:03,286
じゃあ、イナの好きな飲み物は何でしょう？トゥドゥン！
Then, what is Ina's favorite drink? Ta-da!

2167
03:41:03,286 --> 03:41:07,086
えーっとね、うわ、何飲んでたっけ？
Let's see... Oh, what was she drinking?

2168
03:41:07,086 --> 03:41:11,386
いっぱいあったの覚えてて。うーん。
I remember there were so many... Hmm...

2169
03:41:11,386 --> 03:41:14,586
チオビタ！チオビタ！
Tiovita! Tiovita!

2170
03:41:14,586 --> 03:41:16,786
No.

2171
03:41:16,786 --> 03:41:21,186
チオ... チオビタドリンク。栄養ドリンク。エナジー...
Tio... Tiovita drink? An energy drink... Energy...

2172
03:41:21,186 --> 03:41:22,286
8.

2173
03:41:22,286 --> 03:41:23,486
7.

2174
03:41:23,486 --> 03:41:24,686
6.

2175
03:41:24,686 --> 03:41:25,686
5.

2176
03:41:25,686 --> 03:41:26,786
4.

2177
03:41:26,786 --> 03:41:27,986
3.

2178
03:41:27,986 --> 03:41:29,186
2.

2179
03:41:29,186 --> 03:41:30,786
1.

2180
03:41:30,786 --> 03:41:34,086
ブブー！あー！
Boo-boo! Ah!

2181
03:41:34,086 --> 03:41:36,786
チオビタ。チオビタ。チオビタD。
Tiovita... Tiovita... Tiovita D.

2182
03:41:36,786 --> 03:41:43,586
私、私、イナ、イナ、私の正解、正解、正解に答えたら1000万くれる？
Ina, Ina, if I get the right answer, will you give me 10 million?

2183
03:41:43,586 --> 03:41:47,386
私に1000万くれる？
Will you give me 10 million?

2184
03:41:47,386 --> 03:41:52,486
すみません、今日のイナのサービスは終了しました。次の機会にまた会いましょう。
I'm sorry, Ina's service for today has ended. Let's meet again next time.

2185
03:41:52,486 --> 03:41:56,086
チオビタ、チオビタ。ドクターペッパー好きそう。
Tiovita, Tiovita... She seems like she'd like Dr Pepper.

2186
03:41:56,086 --> 03:41:58,286
あ、わかった。アーニャ、も、も、も。
Oh, I got it. Anya, mo-mo-mo...

2187
03:41:58,286 --> 03:42:02,186
絶対チオビタDでしょ？チオビタ。
It's definitely Tiovita D, right? Tiovita.

2188
03:42:02,186 --> 03:42:03,986
ブブー。
Boo-boo.

2189
03:42:03,986 --> 03:42:08,786
えー。
Ehhh.

2190
03:42:08,786 --> 03:42:11,886
え、コーヒー、コーヒー。
Eh, coffee, coffee.

2191
03:42:11,886 --> 03:42:14,086
どんなコーヒー？
What kind of coffee?

2192
03:42:14,086 --> 03:42:20,086
コーヒー、うーん。
Coffee... Hmm...

2193
03:42:20,086 --> 03:42:21,286
カフェオレ。
Cafe au lait.

2194
03:42:21,286 --> 03:42:23,786
ラテ、ラテ、ラテ。
Latte, latte, latte.

2195
03:42:23,786 --> 03:42:26,786
ブブブブー！
Boo-boo-boo-boo!

2196
03:42:26,786 --> 03:42:29,986
残念でした、みんな。
Too bad, everyone.

2197
03:42:29,986 --> 03:42:33,686
ブラック！ブラック！
Black! Black!

2198
03:42:34,686 --> 03:42:36,486
フラペチーノじゃない？
Isn't it a Frappuccino?

2199
03:42:36,486 --> 03:42:38,986
ヨーグルトとブルーベリー。ヨーグルトとブルーベリードリンク。
Yogurt and blueberry. Yogurt and blueberry drink.

2200
03:42:38,986 --> 03:42:43,186
いや皆さん、なんでブラックコーヒーがオプションにないんですか？
Wait, everyone, why is black coffee not even in your options?

2201
03:42:43,186 --> 03:42:47,886
え！待って、ちょっと待って。本当に思ったんだけど、イナ本当に思ったんだけど。
Wait, hold on. I actually thought of that. Ina, I really thought of that, but...

2202
03:42:47,886 --> 03:42:52,886
何でブラック以外の色んなコーヒーが出てたんですけど。
You guys came up with all these other coffees besides black!

2203
03:42:52,886 --> 03:43:02,886
いや思った。いやマジでブラックコーヒーね、思ったんだけど、ホロライブ確率的にブラックコーヒー好きな人は少ないから、確率的に。
No, I did. Seriously, I thought of black coffee, but statistically in Hololive, very few people like black coffee.

2204
03:43:02,886 --> 03:43:04,486
早口だな。
She's such a fast talker.

2205
03:43:04,486 --> 03:43:05,486
だから...
So...

2206
03:43:05,486 --> 03:43:07,186
早口。
Fast talker.

2207
03:43:07,186 --> 03:43:08,786
だから、マジで！
So, seriously!

2208
03:43:08,786 --> 03:43:21,186
I used my brain cell, and then think about the percentage of someone liking a black coffee. And I went for the percentage, or the higher percentage answer.

2209
03:43:21,186 --> 03:43:23,086
残念でした。
Too bad.

2210
03:43:23,086 --> 03:43:25,686
えー。
Ehhh.

2211
03:43:25,686 --> 03:43:29,086
そんな。そんな。
No way. No way.

2212
03:43:29,086 --> 03:43:30,186
しくしく。
*sob sob*

2213
03:43:30,186 --> 03:43:31,386
次の機会に。
Next time.

2214
03:43:31,386 --> 03:43:34,686
うわー！
Waaaaah!

2215
03:43:34,686 --> 03:43:37,686
Wait, I must go fulfill my mission.

2216
03:43:37,686 --> 03:43:42,786
I will see you at the finals, Anya, soon.

2217
03:43:42,786 --> 03:43:44,486
Okay. Bye-bye. / Bye-bye.

2218
03:43:44,486 --> 03:43:46,186
時間がない。時間がない。
No time, no time.

2219
03:43:46,186 --> 03:43:51,686
は、は、は、どうしよう。どうしよう。ここで、ここでどうしよう。
Ah, what should I do? What should I do? Here, what should I do here?

2220
03:43:58,286 --> 03:44:03,486
「発光ってどうすればできるんだっけ？」
\"How do you get glowing?\"

2221
03:44:03,486 --> 03:44:06,486
「もう一個、発光を付けたら良くない？」
\"Wouldn't it be better if we added another glowing?\"

2222
03:44:12,686 --> 03:44:15,986
あ、これが早い。オッケーオッケー。
Oh, this is faster. Okay, okay.

2223
03:44:15,986 --> 03:44:18,686
I just need to get to 50.

2224
03:44:18,686 --> 03:44:22,686
How am I going to spend 75,000?

2225
03:44:24,686 --> 03:44:31,686
I'm going to leash chickens to the world, I'm sorry. It's the only way.

2226
03:44:46,686 --> 03:44:50,986
これ、欲しくないんだ。
I don't want this.

2227
03:44:52,686 --> 03:44:55,686
\"Buy something more expensive.\" Oh, right.

2228
03:44:55,686 --> 03:44:59,686
Oh, you're right.

2229
03:45:01,486 --> 03:45:03,686
光ってる場合じゃない。
This is not the time to be glowing.

2230
03:45:03,694 --> 03:50:03,702
Error processing subtitles for this segment.

2231
03:50:03,702 --> 03:55:03,710
Error processing subtitles for this segment.

